videos.description: Jayson Tatum stop and fakes the jump shot to free up space and makes a nice pass to Luke Kornet for the easy finish inside.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum flips sweet dime to Kornet for the finish) 2021/03/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum flips sweet dime to Kornet for the finish

videos.description: Luka Doncic goes behind the back and then uses a step-back move to lose the defender and drain a 3-pointer for the Mavs.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Luka shakes defender to tickle the twine from 3) 2021/03/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Luka shakes defender to tickle the twine from 3

videos.description: Jayson Tatum gets the inbound pass and burns his defender as he speeds to the basket to throw down an emphatic dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum blows by defender for powerful slam) 2021/03/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum blows by defender for powerful slam

videos.description: Luka Doncic goes behind his back then steps back to drain a 3-pointer from way beyond the 3-point line.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Doncic drains unreal step-back from deep) 2021/03/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Doncic drains unreal step-back from deep

videos.description: Luka Doncic goes deep in his bag as he punishes multiple Celtics defenders with step-back moves en route to five 3-pointers in the Mavs' 113-108 win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Luka's step-back 3 unstoppable vs. Celtics) 2021/03/31 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Luka's step-back 3 unstoppable vs. Celtics
